01:48:49.070 --> 01:48:51.070
So for a while, they called me Squant P.

01:48:51.070 --> 01:48:54.070
And then they sort of broke it down to Squant.

01:48:54.070 --> 01:48:57.070
S-Q-U-A-N-T.

